ld and silver coins, so what do you instruct us or what should we work for?\u201d The\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40035,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/05\/12\/thankful-qalb\/","url_meta":{"origin":38075,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Gratitude: What kind of wealth should we acquire?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 12, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cDestruction is in the desire for gold and silver.\u201d Umar said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what kind of wealth should we seek?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cA tongue of remembrance, a grateful heart, and a believing\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21935,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/02\/15\/comprehensive-and-concise-dua\/","url_meta":{"origin":38075,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Use comprehensive and concise supplications","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 15, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, entered my room while I was praying and I was slow to take care of his need. The Prophet said, \u201cO Aisha, you must use comprehensive and concise supplications.\u201d When I finished, I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what are\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u062